FILE HANDLING IN JAVA:
========================

Streams->sequence of data ex..file,audio,images etc.
#types: 1] byte Stream
             a)Input
             b)Output
        2] character
              a)Reader
              b)Writer

    Perform input/output with this Streams   
    Abstraction that Java provides
    connected to physical devices like keyboard

java impelements these within class hierachy in java.io package

# Systen.in -> 'in' is type InputStream  ->keyboard
  [PrintStream]
# Systen.out -> 'out' is type OutputStream  ->console
# Systen.error -> error stream  -> console






